animeTitle: I Say Go, the System Says Go Die
otherNames: My System Wants Me Dead, I Just Want To Live A Simple Life, I Say Go the System Says Go Die, Ta Muốn An Tĩnh, Hệ Thống Lại Bắt Ta Tìm Chết, Wo Shuo Gou, Xitong Shuo Gou Dai, Wǒ Shuō Gǒu, Xìtǒng Shuō Gǒu Dài, おまかせ修練に殺されかけています, 我说苟，系统说狗带
synopsis: "Ding! This is the Intelligent DEF Cultivation System. There is a prompt. During the cultivation, you will lose control of your body..." After getting the Intelligent DEF Cultivation System, Pei Ling thought he could improve his strength secretly and become the strongest cultivator one day, but... "Ding! Detected a lack of a female partner. The system is searching one for you..." And then, Pei Ling helplessly watched himself kick open the door of the saintess' room and rape her unconscious body.
